text: Helcystogramma albinervis is a moth in the family Gelechiidae. It was described by Aleksey Maksimovich Gerasimov in 1929. It is found in Hungary, Romania, Slovakia, Poland, Latvia, Ukraine and Russia.Fauna Europaea The wingspan is about 15 mm.Lepiforum.de ==References== Category:Moths described in 1929 albinervis Category:Moths of Europe Category:Moths of Russia
